Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Interface LitmusPPCListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
LitmusPPCBaseListener
public interface LitmusPPCListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by LitmusPPCParser.
